ondays and Fridays. To learn more about Melanie, <a href=\"http://rockypointwellness.com/melanie.html\">Click here</a>.</em></strong>', 'Giving Advice To Your Counsellor???   5 Types of Feedback That Can Be Very Helpful', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '75-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-02 17:24:42', '2017-10-02 17:24:42', '', 75, 'http://rockypointwellness.com/blog/2017/10/02/75-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
